      "instruction": "<p>To serve, layer the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>,<strong> tomatoey croutons</strong>, <strong>diced avocado</strong>, <strong>smoky mushrooms </strong>and<strong> charred corn </strong>in rows</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> ranch-style dressing </strong>over everything – this is your <strong>plant-based cobb salad</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
